---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import img from '~/assets/tito_xd-cafe-manager-by-frankuwu.png';
import { SiteDescription, SiteTitle } from '~/config';
import MarkdownLayout from '~/layouts/MarkdownLayout.astro';
---

<MarkdownLayout
	title={SiteTitle}
	description={SiteDescription}
	hide={['title', 'comments']}
	currentNav="Home"
>
	<section class="home-intro">
		<Picture
			class="home-intro__art"
			src={img}
			formats={['avif', 'webp']}
			alt="Tito_XD original character coffee master version by Frankuwu"
			loading="eager"
		/>
		<div class="home-intro__copy">
			<h1 class="home-intro__title">路上辛苦了<br />喝点什么？</h1>
			<div class="home-intro__body">
				<p>我是 Tito_XD，今日轮值的店长，也可以叫我头头。</p>
				<p>又是新的一年，忙忙碌碌就这样开始了。</p>
				<p>总归还是生活碎碎念。如果我的寥寥几字也能让你驻足停看，那也不错，谢谢。</p>
				<p class="home-intro__links">
					<a class="ui-type-link" href="/posts/rewind-2025">
						<span class="ui-type-link__text">2025 年的 REWIND 在这里</span>
					</a>
					<span>，</span>
					<a class="ui-type-link" href="/posts/onward-2026">
						<span class="ui-type-link__text">2026 年的 ONWARD 在这里</span>
					</a>
					<span>。欢迎光临，请开心。</span>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</MarkdownLayout>

<style>
	.home-intro {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.home-intro__art {
		max-width: min(100%, 17.5rem);
		justify-self: center;
	}

	.home-intro__copy {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.9rem;
		max-width: 34rem;
	}

	.home-intro__title {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.8vw, 3.4rem);
		line-height: 0.98;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		text-wrap: balance;
	}

	.home-intro__body {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.home-intro__body p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.82;
	}

	.home-intro__links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.1rem 0.3rem;
	}

	.home-intro__links a {
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		.home-intro {
			grid-template-columns: minmax(13rem, 17.5rem) minmax(0, 1fr);
			gap: 1.35rem;
		}

		.home-intro__art {
			justify-self: start;
		}
	}
</style>
